      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HURRICANE (3) turned in a strong 28.12 despite finishing sixth in a Group Listed at Bendigo last start. Has the ability and expected to go close. OVERLAND BOY (1) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (35.15) at this track. Form at the trip sound including nine wins. Will give a great sight again. UPENDED (7) jumped cleanly from the rails to lead much the way when second (27.80) at Bendigo in a Group Listed over 500m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. Expecting another good run. GIACOMO (4) did a good job to finish third last time out over 525m at this track (30.39) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
